项目支出导致。 值得注意的是，特斯拉在营收保持增长的同时，其毛利率却在继续下滑。财报显示，特斯拉第三季度毛利率进一步下滑至 17.9%，较二季度的 18.2% 下滑了 0.3 个百分点，创 4 年新低。 在外界看来，特斯拉利润率的下滑主要受其今年来的大规模降价影响。不过，特斯拉 CEO 马斯克却表示，他愿意牺牲盈利能力来换取销量。「愿意在‘动荡时期’再次下调电动汽车的价格，尽管这会影响公司毛利率，但愿意牺牲毛利率换取销量增长。」马斯克曾公开表示。 毛利率创 4 年新低！特斯拉三季度净利润同比下滑 44%，马斯克称将坚持继续降价 | 每经网 (nbd.com.cn)"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-40140d22b13bcf8b2bcae8c46d677540_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "35 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/626901506"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIlsH94aH5xvAPEAMaCTEwMTU5MDU1NiDw1cSpBjAAOM0BQCZyCTYyNjkwMTUwNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1697832480.458892", "card_id": "Q_627013905", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "S13 瑞士轮胜者组 GEN 1:0 击败 T1，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-26e07343d000bad26d3ba07a802d652c_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "35 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/627013905"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IlsH94aH5xvAPEAMaCTEwMTYxNTM2MiDPh8mpBjAAOEpAJ3IJNjI3MDEzOTA1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1697832480.459204", "card_id": "Q_606956329", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 35}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "能否通过基因编辑在短时间改造人类?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "例如在生化危机中感染 t 病毒后几小时内进化成另一生物，或像少年骇客一样短时间改变自身基因来变成其他生物"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-351e1a8bd5b04be650a2afb402b44fa8_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B73